記者會一樣，幫手足行為消毒。等大家唔洗怕我地會步黃背心後塵，等世界清楚知道我地嘅攻擊目標，唔係亂咁黎"},{"pid":"9a3756212a70e3f6f0d2e506d177f020318ec040","tid":1614906,"uid":19255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fb66b4664b2355ce4ee0d8cdc863480247797df0","tid":1614906,"uid":199235,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7e2a4efabfc707cf05a7572898ed5a024d5df6c3","tid":1614906,"uid":19255,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fd1646f136d247871ddae8a3e828d060cc6effb5","tid":1614906,"uid":199235,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:42:22.000Z","msg":"good..但唔駛登報既, 好多外媒會幫手宣傳..<br />\n做好文宣..同埋前線真係配合先ok"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:43:38.000Z","msg":"登報有震撼力，會吸引到更多人自己搵我地行動守則黎睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:55:46.000Z","msg":"如果十幾年前..登報當然好, 我只係好奇今時今日仲有幾多人買報紙睇ja  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n登報講出黎好好聽, 但擔心個效果無咁大威力..不如試下互聯網既威力, facebook, ig, google, <br />\n或將d錢用多d 係抗爭及補捕人仕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:58:41.000Z","msg":"我地前兩次登報都好成功，可以make noise，啲錢可以兩邊都用，冇衝突"},{"pid":"d0f0e7f2ffb13e9ef8f9e622efd39f1df0de0b13","tid":1614906,"uid":47208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a8157bae0a37def30ed479b796ffa976de893a31","tid":1614906,"uid":19255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b795484f69e5e8bc12411ba32bd8bf1c6802cc4","tid":1614906,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:45:58.000Z","msg":"登報不如youtube twitter落ad"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:48:57.000Z","msg":"都可以，登報都係途徑姐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:58:41.000Z","msg":"太密會麻目左<br />\n同埋全球登報講緊幾百萬<br />\n<br />\n我認同登報絕對有用<br />\n不過對比起g20同10.1 國慶<br />\n<br />\n平日登報既性價比唔係太值得<br />\n<br />\n巴打你提議好好，<br />\n不過國際線Twitter 更需要人<br />\n而筆錢暫時最好係先流向星火"},{"pid":"cd5abcf59719003f9b70dbd7aa9c1ad80d5bc62e","tid":1614906,"uid":19255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d0f0e7f2ffb13e9ef8f9e622efd39f1df0de0b13","tid":1614906,"uid":47208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a8157bae0a37def30ed479b796ffa976de893a31","tid":1614906,"uid":19255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b795484f69e5e8bc12411ba32bd8bf1c6802cc4","tid":1614906,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:45:58.000Z","msg":"登報不如youtube twitter落ad"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:48:57.000Z","msg":"都可以，登報都係途徑姐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:58:41.000Z","msg":"太密會麻目左<br />\n同埋全球登報講緊幾百萬<br />\n<br />\n我認同登報絕對有用<br />\n不過對比起g20同10.1 國慶<br />\n<br />\n平日登報既性價比唔係太值得<br />\n<br />\n巴打你提議好好，<br />\n不過國際線Twitter 更需要人<br />\n而筆錢暫時最好係先流向星火"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:02:07.000Z","msg":"我原意就係希望一舖過等全世界知我地有明確的攻擊目標，唔洗次次都爆完舖又要一堆人去文宣澄清。<br />\n雖然貴但係我覺得好有效。"},{"pid":"8da1cf4d728a4fcabc4b3d6b0627dda6eee4c6ba","tid":1614906,"uid":19255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:09:39.000Z","msg":"其實好簡單一點：<br />\n<br />\n我地眼中見到係藍絲比人以武制暴；<br />\n外人眼中就係平民比我地打。<br />\n<br />\n我地眼中我地爆中資舖頭；<br />\n外人眼中我地無差別破壞。<br />\n<br />\n我重申登報只係一個文宣途徑，雖然貴，但可以吸引注意力。我地都可以先加強文宣，依家係明顯唔夠，尤其係國際線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07fc4c4687d697303bdfa346d984088189cba8d7","tid":1614906,"uid":6833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:15:43.000Z","msg":"都係要做好文宣"},{"pid":"f87ab155a43dc8675de9be9f8e01b50616a0b1d7","tid":1614906,"uid":23046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:29:21.000Z","msg":"上面有人講到<br />\n話用網上平台/文宣去做<br />\n唔係唔得<br />\n但因為我地冇大台<br />\n咁樣各自傳 訊息既內容/格式會有出入<br />\n雖然而家網上資訊係多人睇d<br />\n但係都登報都仲係一個比較formal啲有代表性既表達方法<br />\n就好似一間公司，要發佈一啲重要方案<br />\n都係會有自己公司專頁/官網去公佈一篇正式文章<br />\n跟住先會再由其下藝人/工作者去make noise/宣揚<br />\n但抗爭者並無大台，亦冇官網專頁等等<br />\n所以登報可以算係我地既正式宣言<br />\n然後再係民間記者會講一次<br />\n跟住先就住正式宣言再去做文宣，網上傳播<br />\n咁樣就可以話比所有人知<br />\n我地抗爭者都係就住呢個大方向去做<br />\n<br />\n如果自己傳自己講，佢地都嘛係會覺得有人守有人唔守<br />\n樓主就係想我地既行動系統化同做到我地係有守則既形象"},{"pid":"e31c3c272eb0b19168428529bdd2373086dbbd1a","tid":1614906,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:30:28.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"b7be10431b9eec27694c7cae9c73be823a270f00","tid":1614906,"uid":254246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:37:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5f956ec7179fd959466bfa052399ec04b59a40a2","tid":1614906,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:39:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e687e6fc265cbf50e2774bc21d62e7fefe8e5a1","tid":1614906,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:41:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5bb8d793c0b48f71f8fd865ebe85df9bf2f79fa","tid":1614906,"uid":23046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:41:47.000Z","msg":"有用po冇人睇？<br />\n樓主自己都唔推？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}